---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Studio — Done-For-You earned media services" description="701am Studio — done-for-you earned-media enrollment fulfillment and organic AI/SEO growth for universities, edtech, and agencies. Inquire for pricing.">
<!-- HERO -->
<header class="ind-hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-atmos"><div class="grid"></div><div class="glow g1"></div><div class="glow g2"></div><div class="glow g3"></div></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="ind-eyebrow"><a class="bk" href="/">701am</a> / Studio</div>
    <h1>Done-for-you earned media &amp; <em class="grad">AI visibility</em>.</h1>
    <p class="isub">Run the full earned-media engine without a full-time team. 701am Studio delivers enrollment growth via <b>Organic SEO</b> &amp; <b>AI Citation Saturation</b> for universities, edtech companies, and the agencies that serve them — scoped, staffed, and managed on your behalf.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-studio"><i class="ti ti-sparkles"></i>Inquire about Studio pricing</a>
      <a href="#services" class="btn btn-soft btn-lg"><i class="ti ti-arrow-down"></i>See what we offer</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- SERVICES -->
<section class="band wrap" id="services">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Studio services</div>
    <h2>Four ways to <em class="grad">work with us</em>.</h2>
    <p>Pick the service that matches your goal — or combine several together.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="studio-cards">
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)">Placements</span>
      <h3>Earned Media Enrollment Fulfillment</h3>
      <p>Full-cycle earned media for enrollment — from data-story research through journalist outreach, placement tracking, and funnel correlation. We find the angles, write the pitches, manage the reporter list, and tie every placement back to inquiry and application movement.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Data-story research &amp; narrative development</li>
        <li>Journalist outreach &amp; reporter relationship management</li>
        <li>Placement tracking &amp; coverage monitoring</li>
        <li>Funnel correlation from placement to inquiry</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>universities, enrollment marketing teams</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">Retainers from $3,500/mo</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Start a conversation <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--amber-soft);color:var(--amber-deep)">Visibility</span>
      <h3>Organic AI/SEO Growth</h3>
      <p>Build the visibility assets — data studies, category-defining content, press coverage — that compound your institution's presence across ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google, and the press simultaneously.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>AI citation strategy &amp; optimization</li>
        <li>Category-defining content &amp; data studies</li>
        <li>Search rank growth &amp; SERP ownership</li>
        <li>Third-party coverage that feeds AI models</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>edtech, agencies, category leaders</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">Retainers from $3,500/mo</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Start a conversation <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)">Authority</span>
      <h3>Rankings &amp; Data Visibility</h3>
      <p>Earn the rankings, outcomes data, and third-party coverage that build category authority and make you the default answer when AI models, journalists, and prospective students evaluate your category.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Program &amp; school rankings strategy</li>
        <li>Outcomes data publishing &amp; distribution</li>
        <li>Third-party directory &amp; review placement</li>
        <li>Competitor displacement through data superiority</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>universities, OPMs</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">Custom, scoped to program count</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Start a conversation <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scard">
      <span class="sc-tag" style="background:var(--green-soft);color:var(--green-deep)">Narrative</span>
      <h3>Content &amp; Thought Leadership</h3>
      <p>Position your leadership and your institution's story in the publications, podcasts, and platforms that your audience already trusts — with the data and rigor that makes coverage stick.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Executive thought leadership &amp; bylines</li>
        <li>Podcast, keynote &amp; panel placement</li>
        <li>Co-published research &amp; whitepapers</li>
        <li>Newsletter and homepage features</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="sc-foot">
        <div class="sc-best">Best for <b>agencies, university leadership</b></div>
        <div class="sc-price">From $2,000/mo</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="sc-cta">Start a conversation <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
<section class="band wrap">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Who it's for</div>
    <h2>Built for teams that need <em class="grad">more than software</em>.</h2>
    <p>701am Studio is for institutions and agencies that want the full engine — configured, managed, and staffed.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="forind" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)">
    <a class="ficard" href="/universities">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--gold-soft);color:var(--gold-deep)"><i class="ti ti-school"></i></div>
      <h3>Universities</h3>
      <p>Your enrollment team knows the programs. We run the earned-media engine that makes them the answer in AI, search, and the press — placements tied to funnel movement, not just impressions.</p>
      <span class="more">For enrollment teams <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></span>
    </a>
    <a class="ficard" href="/edtech">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)"><i class="ti ti-device-laptop"></i></div>
      <h3>Edtech &amp; OPMs</h3>
      <p>Your category authority is a competitive advantage. Studio builds the data studies, trade coverage, and AI citations that make you the default choice when institutions evaluate your category.</p>
      <span class="more">For edtech companies <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></span>
    </a>
    <a class="ficard" href="/agencies">
      <div class="fi" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)"><i class="ti ti-briefcase"></i></div>
      <h3>Agencies</h3>
      <p>Add an earned-media arm to your agency overnight. Studio runs per-client, isolated, and white-label — you keep the strategy and the relationship, we deliver the placements and visibility data.</p>
      <span class="more">For agencies <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i></span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TRUST NOTE -->
<section class="band wrap" style="padding-top:0">
  <div class="studio-note">
    <i class="ti ti-shield-check"></i>
    <div>
      <strong>On independence.</strong> 701am's rankings, data, and editorial are independent and are not for sale. Studio services — earned media campaigns, AI visibility, and content partnerships — are kept separate from that editorial work, and sponsored material is always labeled. Our data is held to the same sourced, no-invented-numbers standard whether it appears in an article or a client report.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TRAINING & WEBINARS -->
<section class="band wrap" id="training">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <div class="sec-eyebrow">Training &amp; Webinars</div>
    <h2>Learn the platform, master the <em class="grad">craft</em>.</h2>
    <p>Get your team up to speed with guided onboarding, live sessions, and direct access to the Studio team.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="training-grid">
    <div class="tcard">
      <div class="tcard-icon" style="background:var(--coral-soft);color:var(--coral-deep)"><i class="ti ti-rocket"></i></div>
      <h3>Onboarding Program</h3>
      <p>Guided setup and configuration for your workspace — connect your CRM, define your programs, set campaign goals, and get your first visibility baseline within a week.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Dedicated onboarding specialist</li>
        <li>Workspace configuration &amp; data connection</li>
        <li>First campaign launched together</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="tcard">
      <div class="tcard-icon" style="background:var(--amber-soft);color:var(--amber-deep)"><i class="ti ti-presentation"></i></div>
      <h3>Live Webinars</h3>
      <p>Weekly live sessions on earned-media strategy, AI visibility tactics, and platform deep-dives. Recorded and available on demand if you can't attend live.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Earned-media strategy &amp; data storytelling</li>
        <li>Platform feature walkthroughs &amp; updates</li>
        <li>Q&amp;A with the Studio team</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="tcard">
      <div class="tcard-icon" style="background:var(--indigo-soft);color:var(--indigo-deep)"><i class="ti ti-book"></i></div>
      <h3>Documentation &amp; Guides</h3>
      <p>Comprehensive docs, playbooks, and best-practice guides covering everything from first setup to advanced campaign orchestration.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Platform documentation &amp; API references</li>
        <li>Earned-media playbooks by segment</li>
        <li>Campaign strategy templates</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="tcard">
      <div class="tcard-icon" style="background:var(--green-soft);color:var(--green-deep)"><i class="ti ti-users"></i></div>
      <h3>Office Hours</h3>
      <p>Direct access to the Studio team for personalized Q&amp;A, campaign strategy reviews, and help troubleshooting your visibility goals.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Weekly slots — first come, first served</li>
        <li>Campaign strategy &amp; performance reviews</li>
        <li>Custom integration or workflow support</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CLOSING -->
<section class="closing">
  <div class="catmos"><div class="cg"></div></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="pill-badge"><span class="tagm">Filed at sunrise</span></div>
    <h2>Let's talk about what you <em class="grad">need</em>.</h2>
    <p>Tell us about your institution or agency — we'll scope a Studio engagement that matches your goals.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"><i class="ti ti-sparkles"></i>Inquire about Studio</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
